- startup code: command line args, workbench startup

- code generator
    - get rid of unneccesary jumps / nop statements
    - proc calls: only save registers that carry live values
    - use movem to save/restore registers
    - constant propagation
    - take full advantage of constants in code generation
    - peephole optimizer
    - address register allocation

- error handling
    - division by zero
    - ON ERROR ...

- modules / units
    - module/unit compilation mode (i.e. create modules in basic)
    - amiga os library support (AmigaBASIC .fd/.bmap compatible ?)

DONE float type
